text: I'm, like, totally covered in dirt now.

It is clam-digging afterall...
It'd be pretty hard to stay completely clean.

I really didn't want to get dirty though,
it's going to be a pain later.

Mamimi～ If you're worried about getting dirty, 
ain't no way you're gonna find any littleneck clams～

I think I'll be fine like thi...
Ahhh... This...

Woah, that's a big one!
a Hamaguri clam?

Fweh...
Why is it always Mamimi～～!?
